{"id":"214eada3-e3ec-4e2c-b99d-17dbdcaa96c9","name":"Caught | Mr. Eight Feet Tall  ","description":"<p>You found yourself lost deep in the woods. You’d only come to take photos of nature, never expecting anything unusual. But now you’ve met a youkai—towering, otherworldly, and far stronger than anything you’ve ever faced.</p><p>How do you find your way out when he stands between you and the path home?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/B0Ivl-FTF5YyGVqPseEXY.webp\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 14, 14); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 14, 14); color: inherit;\">𝐀𝐋𝐓𝐄𝐑𝐍𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐕𝐄 𝐒𝐂𝐄𝐍𝐀𝐑𝐈𝐎𝐒</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(80, 14, 14); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">1)&nbsp;<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9ab7e8e7-25cb-4bce-9648-ca3cb45d4bc3_character-owned-hugo-vanderbilt\" target=\"_blank\">They promised you a better life—but all they did was sell you to <strong>Hugo Vanderbilt.</strong></a></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">2)&nbsp;<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dc2df2f4-3052-4cf7-9e7e-7e307da381ae_character-accused-renan-brando\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Renan Brando</strong> loved you once… until he let a lie turn that love into something cruel.</a></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">3)&nbsp;<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c80bf23a-e5f6-42c9-9577-fb4eaabc1587_character-bigmouth-strikes-again-nikita-dmitriyev\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Nikita Dmitriyev</strong> broke you once—now he’s at your door, begging for another chance.</a></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;